account.descriptionLink:
The goal of this proposal is to swap 40% of the partner tokens into ai16z.

We've always had very thin liquidity under the token, but it's gotten to the point where the price can be drastically manipulated by one big selloff.

In order to ensure that our token survives while we build, we need to break through the wall in single sided liquidity against our token.

This is not ideal for anyone, but we can buy back partner tokens when we are in a more optimal position.
account.name: Swap 40% of treasury into ai16z
